Docs.summary: Contains values that each expression class uses to denote the operation it represents. The property of an can be retrieved to determine which operation that expression represents.

remarks.format: ## Remarks Use the <xref:System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbExpressionKind> enumeration to specify the various kinds of expressions. The Members table lists the functions that are members of this class and the type of expressions they specify.
